  </titlealts>
  <body>

  <p>
      <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_activity_frequency">ACTIVITY FREQUENCY</xref>
 describes the interval at which an 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_activity">ACTIVITY</xref>
 or event takes place.  </p>
  <p>
      <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_activity_frequency">ACTIVITY FREQUENCY</xref>
 may be used to identify the frequency of when a 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_prescribed_item">PRESCRIBED ITEM</xref>
 is to be taken by a 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
, or the period of time between repeating 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_out-patient_appointment">Out-Patient Appointments</xref>
.  </p>

